{"tid":756455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"81歲支那廢老，聲稱為拜山，想長居香港","createTime":"2018-07-26T05:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T08:00:11.000Z","uid":29314,"like":18,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"23dca20f1303af7b82f85f7be4a55c78bde3e1f5","tid":756455,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"「今年81歲的梁老伯，在香港出生，20歲時到內地參軍，之後再無返港。現在，他想返港居住，因為父親葬在香港，出於孝心，他想恢復香港永久居民的身份，以便去父親墳墓致祭。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩屌，仆街得佢，<br />\n<br />\n幾十年黎一蚊稅都無交過。<br />\n<br />\n臨老想落黎搶公屋、拎綜援、拎免費醫療、仲想之後叫埋一家大細落黎團聚。<br />\n<br />\n你要拜山，挖返個墳頭出黎畀返佢係支那慢慢拜啦！"},{"pid":"e997d731d6775c101cd3644e995ad608c05f038d","tid":756455,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"拜你老母"},{"pid":"6e835c88891859b9bff47c7e7e8876693d85b2e9","tid":756455,"uid":52459,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:38:55.000Z","msg":"老嘢，咪話老夫唔教你，你結束自己生命就可以團聚架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be73eb8113c0acac30a40c9452617fb3d724600b","tid":756455,"uid":65128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:40:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f47cec40e0b593e63554272094a8f005b40b07f7","tid":756455,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df23802d729975d8e950ed3886bb58c22ff67a8b","tid":756455,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:41:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6414e46f92bb8561a927364e695e801f81de85c7","tid":756455,"uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:41:25.000Z","msg":"點解佢會冇左香港身分證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9424d9e192bab861c2828dadce8e6714d8235de7","tid":756455,"uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6414e46f92bb8561a927364e695e801f81de85c7","tid":756455,"uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:41:25.000Z","msg":"點解佢會冇左香港身分證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"抵壘政策<br />\n<br />\n1974年11月，香港政府宣佈實施抵壘政策，中國非法入境者若在偷渡到香港後能抵達市區，便可在香港居留，如果偷渡者在邊境範圍被執法人員截獲，則會被遣返大陸。當局亦因此加強在邊境的管制，以減少非法入境者進入市區的機會。 <br />\n<br />\n1979年，中國開始實施改革開放，政治環境開始變得寬鬆，但中國大陸居民非法入境香港情況越來越嚴重。1980年10月23日，香港政府宣佈取消抵壘政策，轉而採取即捕即解政策。所有非法入境者一經發現，即須被遣返中國大陸。"},{"pid":"b2e3bbc7b4d72075b0e5b612d8e32da28904685c","tid":756455,"uid":60137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:46:23.000Z","msg":"拜山就無喇，掟你隻廢老落海比人拜就得"},{"pid":"82d8b166009d101a7bbebe07f266c5131fae2d6f","tid":756455,"uid":476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"[2010-12-06] <a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2010/12/06/HH1012060004.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2010%2F12%2F06%2FHH1012060004.htm&d=8FrzdiQ2b%2F56ccVZZcMyFOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=3aefd130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2010/12/06/HH1012060004.htm</a><br />\n你班五毛好鍾意耐唔耐貼下舊文出黎挑釁下民眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d66d0b9a7951236a31918fa7a135309685d5fb2","tid":756455,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"佢唔係要落嚟香港團聚<br />\n佢應該要落去地獄同佢屋企人團聚"},{"pid":"d13317523abf96419b059295a08e12163255f87e","tid":756455,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[2010-12-06] <a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2010/12/06/HH1012060004.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2010%2F12%2F06%2FHH1012060004.htm&d=8FrzdiQ2b%2F56ccVZZcMyFOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=3aefd130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2010/12/06/HH1012060004.htm</a><br />\n你班五毛好鍾意耐唔耐貼下舊文出黎挑釁下民眾<img